OL,3,CCouncillor resigns following
OL,4,Cinvestigation into antisemitic tweets
OL,6,FThe Mayor of Bath has resigned after
OL,7,Fbeing suspended from the Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrat party, following retweets
OL,9,Fabout the arson attack on ambulances
OL,10,Frun by a Jewish charity.
OL,12,FDr Bharat Pankhania, the 798th Mayor
OL,13,Fof Bath, retweeted a post on his
OL,14,Fpersonal account on X which called the
OL,15,Farson attack in Golders Green an
OL,16,FIsraeli false flag operation, along
OL,17,Fwith two posts suggesting it was
OL,18,Finsurance fraud.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
