OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774901153
OL,3,CCouncillor resigns following
OL,4,Cinvestigation into antisemitic tweets
OL,6,FHe has since deleted the retweets and
OL,7,Fpublished a full apology on X calling
OL,8,Fthe tweets "abhorrent."
OL,10,FIn his apology posted on X, Dr
OL,11,FPankhania said: "I have been made
OL,12,Faware that I have reposted or replied
OL,13,Fto some posts which have never aligned
OL,14,Fto my values and beliefs, and which
OL,15,Fare abhorrent.
OL,17,F"I am incredibly apologetic that I
OL,18,Fhave not lived up to the standards I
OL,19,Fset myself. I have of course deleted
OL,20,Fthem, and I wish to apologise
OL,21,Funreservedly."
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@WO]sD@QOU}D@NO]
