OL,3,CCouncillor resigns following
OL,4,Cinvestigation into antisemitic tweets
OL,6,FIn a statement, Bath and North East
OL,7,FSomerset Liberal Democrat group said,
OL,8,F"Cllr Bharat Pankhania has offered his
OL,9,Fresignations from the position of
OL,10,FMayor of Bath and from the Liberal
OL,11,FDemocrat Group on Bath and North East
OL,12,FSomerset Council, from which he had
OL,13,Falready been suspended.
OL,15,F"Both these resignations have been
OL,16,Faccepted.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
