CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774901153
OL,3,CCouncillor resigns following
OL,4,Cinvestigation into antisemitic tweets
OL,6,F"Cllr Pankhania again apologised for
OL,7,Fhis interactions on X, and reiterated
OL,8,Fthat he has spent his life working
OL,9,Fwith all communities, whilst
OL,10,Facknowledging the hurt he had caused.
OL,12,F"In resigning, Cllr Pankhania is
OL,13,Ftaking clear personal responsibility
OL,14,Ffor his actions.
OL,16,FAs a Group and as a Party, we reject
OL,17,Fdiscrimination wherever it occurs and
OL,18,Freiterate our stance against
OL,19,Fantisemitism."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
