OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774901153
OL,3,CCouncillor resigns following
OL,4,Cinvestigation into antisemitic tweets
OL,6,FThe four ambulances were set on fire
OL,7,Fin Golders Green, an area in London
OL,8,Fwith a large Jewish community, in the
OL,9,Fearly hours of March 23.
OL,11,FPolice are treating it as an
OL,12,Fantisemitic hate crime.
OL,14,FTwo men who were arrested in
OL,15,Fconnection with the incident on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of arson with intent to
OL,17,Fendanger life have now been released
OL,18,Fon strict bail conditions while the
OL,19,Finvestigation continues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
